    "- A coin with probability to get tail = 0.5\n",
    "    - Toss until you get a tail\n",
    "    - How many time will you get tail\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Solution 1\n",
    "- Probability Tree\n",
    "\n",
    "<img src=\"./img/1.jpg\" width=\"500\"/>\n",
    "\n",
    "- Name x = number of times to get 1 tail\n",
    "    + $E(X)\\ =\\ 1*0.5 + 2*0.5^2 + 3*0.5^3 + ... = 2$ "
   ]
